divs: sighting detailsi left my house at approx. 7:30 p.m. last night to go shopping. i noticed two unusual cloud-like streaks in the sky, almost looked like they were lights coming down. i was looking up only because i saw unusual lights in that same direction on saturday, nov. 16th. i returned from shopping close to 9 p.m., and i could still see these streaks, so they were definately not trails from a plane. my husband thinks some one is having a grand opening in the area and using beacon lights in the sky. i am approx 9 miles north\northwest of philadelphia, near the fort washington turnpike interchange, these lights\streaks appear south and west of my location. i did not look for the lights after 9 p.m.
